## SQLi Detection Patterns

| Pattern | Regex | Severity |
|---------|-------|----------|
| Single quote / comment | `'`, `--`, `#` | LOW |
| Boolean logic | `OR\s+1=1`, `AND\s+1=1` | MEDIUM |
| UNION SELECT | `UNION\s+SELECT` | HIGH |
| Time-delay attack | `SLEEP\(`, `WAITFOR\s+DELAY` | HIGH |
| System table access | `information_schema`, `sysobjects` | HIGH |
| Data exfiltration confirmed | Large result set from `users` table | CRITICAL |

---

## Severity Classification

| Level | Meaning | Action |
|-------|---------|--------|
| LOW | Single suspicious character (e.g. lone quote) | Log only |
| MEDIUM | Basic injection pattern (e.g. `OR 1=1`) | Log + CloudWatch metric |
| HIGH | Successful UNION-based injection detected | Log + SNS alert |
| CRITICAL | Data exfiltration confirmed | Log + SNS alert + DynamoDB |

