## Lambda Function — How It Works

```
Kinesis Stream (WAF logs)
        │
        ▼
  Lambda triggered
        │
        ▼
  Parse log entry
  (source IP, URI, query string, user-agent)
        │
        ▼
  Apply regex patterns
        │
    ┌───┴───┐
  Match?   No match → log as CLEAN, exit
    │
    ▼
  Classify severity
  (LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH / CRITICAL)
        │
        ▼
  HIGH or CRITICAL?
    ├── Yes → Publish to SNS topic
    │         Write to DynamoDB
    └── No  → Write to CloudWatch metric only
```

