## Lambda vs. GuardDuty — Complementary Coverage

| | Lambda | GuardDuty |
|--|--------|-----------|
| What it detects | SQLi patterns in HTTP payloads | Infrastructure anomalies and known bad IPs |
| Data source | WAF logs via Kinesis | CloudTrail, VPC Flow Logs, DNS |
| Detection speed | < 2 seconds | Minutes |
| Customisable | Yes (you write the rules) | No (managed by AWS) |
| Best for | Payload-level detection | Behavioural / infrastructure-level detection |

